# Phase 4: Rider-Customer Real-Time Sync (Current Plan)

The objective is to connect the Customer app, Backend, and Rider app so that new orders are instantly broadcasted to active riders, riders can accept orders, and customers can track the rider's progress in real time.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> Since the Rider app currently relies on mock data and no authentication, we will implement a basic Phone-based Login for Riders on the backend (similar to the Customer OTP logic). Please confirm if you want Riders to use OTP login or a simpler login mechanism for now.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend (`backend-api`)

#### [MODIFY] [src/orders/order.entity.ts](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/orders/order.entity.ts)
- Add a ManyToOne relation for [Rider](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/riders/rider.entity.ts#3-44) so we can attach a rider to an order.

#### [MODIFY] [src/riders/riders.module.ts](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/riders/riders.module.ts) & Add `riders.service.ts`
- Implement basic rider retrieval and creation methods ([findByPhone](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/users/users.service.ts#17-20), [create](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/products/products.controller.ts#25-28)).

#### [MODIFY] [src/auth/auth.controller.ts](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/auth/auth.controller.ts) & [src/auth/auth.service.ts](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/auth/auth.service.ts)
- Add `POST /auth/rider/login-otp` and `POST /auth/rider/verify-otp` to grant JWTs with `role: 'rider'`.

#### [MODIFY] [src/orders/orders.controller.ts](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/orders/orders.controller.ts) & [src/orders/orders.service.ts](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/orders/orders.service.ts)
- **GET /orders/pending**: Endpoint for Riders to fetch currently unassigned orders.
- **POST /orders/:id/accept**: Endpoint for Riders to accept an order. This sets `riderId`, updates status, and broadcasts to the customer.
- In [placeOrder](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/orders/orders.service.ts#22-96), add logic to broadcast the new order via websockets.

#### [MODIFY] [src/orders/orders.gateway.ts](file:///d:/mart/baldia-mart/backend-api/src/orders/orders.gateway.ts)
- Add `joinRidersRoom` subscription.
- Add `emitNewOrder` method to broadcast newly placed orders to the `riders_room`.

